snippet.title: TRANSFORMERS CRASH COMBINER FORCE WAVE 2 SKYHAMMER UNBOXING Transformers Robots in Disguise Toys
snippet.description:
ToyTimeTV unboxes Wave 2 Transformers Robots in Disguise RID Crash combiner SKYHAMMER. In this toy review we show you the new Combiner force Autobot Skyhammer who is a combiner force of Skyledge and Stormhammer. He is one cool looking Autobot. Wave 3 which is the new release has Shocknado which is the decepticon vierson of Skyhammer. Warnado is Stormhammer and Shockdrive is Skysledge. Its amazing but the only difference is the coloring on the plastic. These combiner force bots are really fun to play with you can combine them with others including Shocknado, Dragbreak, Primestrong, and Bumbleside. Some of the crazy combination your can make are Skynado, Primehammer, etc the list goes on and one. What happens when you crash and combine forces with Transformers: Robots in Disguise Skysledge and Stormhammer figures? No, not a traffic jam. You get an awesome two bot Skyhammer Crash Combiner figure. This Crash Combiner two pack features one Skysledge figure and one Stormhammer figure. Crash these figures together in one awesome step to form a Skyhammer combiner robot. Combine these figures with other Crash Combiner figures to form different 2-bot combinations. The Skysledge figure converts from robot to jet in 1step. Stormhammer figure converts from robot to jet in 3 steps. Scan the Autobot shield in combiner mode to unlock the Skyhammer character in the mobile app. Together, Skysledge and Stormhammer form the awesome high-diving Autobot patrol unit the mighty Skyhammer! Crash and combine, it’s Skyhammer time. We lvoe the Transformers combiner force robots on Toytimetv.
